## v2.0.0 (2026-03-25)

**Changed by:** ProjectHephaestus Issue #41, PR #73 -- src-layout migration
**Verification:** verified-local

### What changed
- Added ProjectHephaestus as second verified project in "Verified On" table
- Added observation that simpler projects (no Dockerfile, no Path(__file__) navigations) require fewer changes
- Updated scope table to show Hephaestus had 46 files (vs Scylla's 197) -- complexity scales with project size
- Added note about CODEOWNERS needing update (missed in v1.0.0)
- Added failed attempt: description fields in pre-commit hooks are easy to miss
- Updated verification to verified-local for both projects

### Why
v1.0.0 was based solely on ProjectScylla (a large project with Docker, CI, custom scripts).
ProjectHephaestus is a smaller utility project -- confirmed the same pattern works but with fewer steps needed.
This validates the skill across different project sizes and complexity levels.

